  "paper_id": "2fe2f849b94cf08b559226bc9d78adcaef5ef186",
  "architecture_summary": "AdaptFormer is a plug-and-play fine-tuning framework for Vision Transformers that replaces the original MLP block with an AdaptMLP bottleneck module consisting of down-projection, ReLU, up-projection, and a scaling factor in parallel with the frozen original MLP. It fine-tunes only the newly added parameters while keeping the pre-trained backbone frozen, aiming for efficient adaptation across image and video recognition tasks.",
